<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV94">
<l>ūṉiṉmēya vāvinīyu ṟakkamōṭu ṇarccinī</l>
<l>āṉiṉmēya vaintunīya vaṟṟuṇiṉṟa tūymainī</l>
<l>vāṉiṉōṭu maṇṇunīva ḷaṅkaṭaṟpa yaṉunī</l>
<l>yāṉunīya taṉṟiyempi rāṉunīyi rāmaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are the life breath that dwells in the body! You are consciousness along with sleep!</l>
<l>You are all five [products] that abide in a cow! You are the purity found in them!</l>
<l>You are the earth along with the sky! You are the wealth in the abundant ocean!</l>
<l>You are me, too! Other than that, You are also our Lord, o Rāma!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
